v2.2alpha - 2011-03-11

	* create development repository https://github.com/mhaller/pyffmpeg 
	  with PyFFmpeg version 2.1 beta as initial version
	  (http://pyffmpeg.googlecode.com/files/pyffmpeg-2.1beta.tar.gz) 

	* updating README file, changing version number for PyFFmpeg to 2.2alpha,
	  update setup.py and pyffmpeg.pyx for current FFmpeg checkout (see version details in README)

	* new functions are 
		get_current_frame_macroblock_types
		get_current_frame_motion_vectors
		get_current_frame_reference_index

	* libavformat/avio.h has changed noticeable

	* add testInstalledPyFFmpeg.py and test.mp4 as test case 